python-codemap install notes
============================
1. Bootstrap once: python3 scripts/generate_codemap.py . --force
2. Add to .gitignore: .claude/codemap.md, .claude/.codemap_hashes.json, .claude/.codemap_data.json
3. In your project CLAUDE.md add a "## Codebase Map" block telling Claude to consult .claude/codemap.md before multi-file work.
4. Install the python-codemap hook (pull.sh add hook python-codemap) to keep the map fresh on edits.
